## 💡 Key Concepts
- `Docker@2` task handles login, build, and push in one task type
- `$(Build.BuildId)` creates a unique, traceable tag per build
- Always tag with both `latest` and the build ID for traceability
- Test the container locally in the pipeline before pushing
